title: History of the Mets in the World Series
text: Blogs History of the Mets in the World Series: The Daily News front and back pages With the Mets winning a fifth National League pennant after besting the Cubs in the NLCS, we take a look back at this franchise's Amazin' World Series history as seen on the front and back pages of the Daily News.
